{"tid":389780,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"22:40【加勒比海盜5：死無對證 2017】","createTime":"2017-09-06T14:11:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T14:45:57.000Z","uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52106a5dad91b0f619de7dd8de291ecd1b6c0be7","tid":389780,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T14:11:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://sites.simbla.com/871f3a54-3131-b616-e5df-b781f31a0a3a/iusee\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsites.simbla.com%2F871f3a54-3131-b616-e5df-b781f31a0a3a%2Fiusee&d=nkbfWGSnA4Gd6TbsJLrb19tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=ea16be26\" target=\"_blank\">http://sites.simbla.com/871f3a54-3131-b616-e5df-b781f31a0a3a/iusee</a><br />\n<br />\n　　故事發生在《加勒比海盜3：世界的盡頭》沉船灣之戰20年後。 男孩亨利（布蘭頓&middot;思懷茲 Brenton Thwaites 飾）隨英國海軍出航尋找被聚魂棺詛咒的父親&ldquo;深海閻王&rdquo;威爾&middot;特納（奧蘭多&middot;布魯姆 Orlando Bloom 飾），卻在百慕大三角遭遇被解封的亡靈薩拉查船長（哈維爾&middot;巴登 Javier Bardem 飾）。獲取自由的薩拉查屠盡加勒比海盜，征服了整個海域，手刃了&ldquo;黑胡子&rdquo;愛德華&middot;蒂奇（伊恩&middot;麥柯肖恩 Ian McShane 飾）的裡海海盜王赫克托&middot;巴博薩船長（傑弗裡&middot;拉什 Geoffrey Rush 飾）在女巫Haifaa Meni(格什菲&middot;法拉哈尼 Golshifteh Farahani 飾)口中得知了薩拉查的真實目的：為尋找他的宿敵傑克船長（約翰尼&middot;德普 Johnny Depp 飾）。海盜的命運皆壓在落魄的老傑克被封印的黑珍珠號，以及天文學家卡琳娜&middot;史密斯（卡雅&middot;斯考達裡奧 Kaya Scodelario 飾）口中的遠古三叉戟上。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/qzp7XwtVw_I/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fqzp7XwtVw_I%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=9cd9ea46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75371512220aef64ff194217184892e3d01fe63c","tid":389780,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T14:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed4253851e91f8e83e7e48530a1b8af348f23a46","tid":389780,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T14:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}